
<p>1Password can now unlock automatically when unlocking your Mac. The feature is now available to 1Password 8 users. You&#8217;ll need to enable it in settings. You can set the “reset” timer between 10 minutes and never.</p>



<p>Of course, this all depends on your own environment and comfort level, but if you find yourself annoyed by having to type your master password more than you&#8217;d like, this is for you.</p>



